2005-11-05

    * Release of version d0.6a (Reborn on birthday)
    
    * Fixed:
    - improved tape emulator (some damned loaders should work now)
    - reduced timeout in device detect and keep long for work (obsoletes TOUT_LONG)
    - "blackscreen" bug in browser

    * New:
    - splitted to two parts, first is in EEPROM, second "boots" into MAPRAM
    - font is in ROM again and should be standard or bold
    - changed some printouts in snaps running etc.
    - ROM paging of +2A/+3 can be disabled
    - removed eject ATAPI device
    - removed screensaver
    - suppress run 128K snap in 48K mode
    - poke manager (support for .pok files and manual entry)
    - browser layout change (file list)
    - improved key repeat
    - full featured data input (no "Hebrew syndrom" :)
    - all keyboard scans are with key repeat
    - strange sounds (key echo and error beep)


2005-02-28
    
    * Release of version d0.5b (Damned IDE devices)

    * New:
    - improved code and logic of IDE devices detection + translation setting
    - 128K SNA
    - snaps with enabled interrupt are synced with it on run


2005-02-20
    
    * Rerelease of version d0.5a (Still alive)

    * Fixed:
    - now uses new bin2tap
    - CRC of ROM is counted with font in RAM (better detection of corruption)
    - find ISO fixed (finally?)

    * New:
    - some parts can be turned on or off (see config.a80)
    - new design, new logo
    - key "R" (reset) together with SS do full reset (inc. font etc.)
    - support for old HDD without LBA
    - 48/128 mode detection, active 128K page detection
    - VRAM switching via "V" key
    - "exteded function meaning" moved from CAPS SHIFT to SYMBOL SHIFT


2004-06-05
    
    * CVS update
    
    * Fixed:
    - "only first 64 MB of CF/HDD" bug


2004-05-26
    
    * CVS update
    
    * Fixed:
    - .Z80 format have swaped regs. A and F, corrected
    - now it take care about page numbers in 48K .Z80


2004-05-13

    * Rerelease of version d0.4b (AS build)

    * New:
    - source code included
    - docs translated to english


